ara","relationship":"trainer"}],"recentEvents":"Talked with Rand about marriage and her desire to be a Wisdom, and dismissed his and the others' claims of seeing a black-cloaked rider."},{"name":"Perrin Aybara","aliases":["Perrin"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Tragedy","currentLocation":"Emond's Field","description":"A strong and kind blacksmith’s son, known for his sense of duty and loyalty to his friends.","relationships":[{"character":"Rand al'Thor","relationship":"friend"},{"character":"Mat Cauthon","relationship":"friend"}],"recentEvents":"Saw a strange rider near the village and discussed the encounter with Rand and Mat."},{"name":"Nynaeve al'Meara","aliases":["Nynaeve"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"The Tragedy","currentLocation":"Emond's Field","description":"A young woman who has aspirations to be the Wisdom and possesses a strong sense of duty and compassion.","relationships":[{"character":"Egwene al'Vere","relationship":"trainer"},{"character":"Rand al'Thor","relationship":"villager"}],"recentEvents":"Saw the mysterious man in black and discussed his sighting with Rand, Mat, and Perrin."},{"name":"Mistress Ayellin","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"this chapter","currentLocation":"Emond's Field","description":"An older woman who was suffering from a fever that Rand and the Wisdom helped to treat.","relationships":[{"character":"Rand al'Thor","relationship":"patient"},{"character":"Nynaeve al'Meara","relationship":"Wisdom providing care"}],"recentEvents":"Suffered from a fever that was treated by Nynaeve and Rand."},{"name":"Mistress Luhhan","aliases":["Master Luhhan"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"this chapter","currentLocation":"Emond's Field","description":"The blacksmith who has been Rand's mentor in smithing and is known for his strong and sturdy hammer.","relationships":[{"character":"Perrin Aybara","relationship":"apprentice"},{"character":"Rand 